import PyPDF2
pdf_path = './18-MassActiv/MassActiv-main/paper.pdf'
with open(pdf_path, 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    text = ''
    for page in reader.pages[:3]:  # Only first 3 pages for now
        text += page.extract_text() + '\n'
print(text[:2000])
